@prefix narr: <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .

GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ArchitectureOverview> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ArchitectureOverview> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#ArchitectureOverview> ;
    narr:childCount "41"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "a8f6c2b6d13585ea28b2f0c9bf94493d1c3f3502" ;
    narr:narration """The architecture has transitioned from a directory-based compilation model to a [transform-based perspective engine](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_TransformOverQuery), where [pure-function workflows](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PureFunctionArchitecture) isolate computation from side effects. Institutional memory is now managed through [group-specific repositories](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_GroupAsRepo), with identity anchored to [phone numbers](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_IdentityViaPhone). Recent refinements (Jul 2026) established a [four-section response structure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerspectiveResponseOrderedByVolatility) that prioritizes [visibility via a complete area index](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_VisibilityInvariantAreaIndex) while allocating [rich-tier slots based on steering weight](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_RichTierBySteeringWeight). The system treats [navigation as the primary read path](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_NavigationReplacesEmbeddedSnapshot), moving away from embedded snapshots. While the [core ontology remains domain-agnostic](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_OntologyDomainAgnostic), the [conviction stack's lack of a temporality axis](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConvictionStackTemporalityGap) remains a critical structural gap, now validated by production failures. The architecture further explores [named advisor perspectives](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_NamedPerspectiveArchitecture) as sub-agents and [in-memory graph storage](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GraphInMemoryStorage) to decouple from GitHub dependencies.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_GroupAsRepo> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Arch_IdentityViaPhone> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CodeAsCompilationOutput> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_CompileTimeActorLens> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ConvictionStackTemporalityGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DataHandlingSubstantiated> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_DigestAsRecognitionAid> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GitHubAsInstitutionalMemory> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_GraphInMemoryStorage> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_ImplicationConceptProvisional> ;
